summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting the redevelopment proposal of Alexander D. Hicks and Nolvia J. Hicks, doing business as Novalco Enterprises to purchase and develop a parcel in the Yesler Atlantic Neighborhood Improvement Project area (Wash. R-5); authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to execute and deliver contracts and deeds; authorizing the Department of Community Development Director to administer the "Contract of Sale of Land"; designating the disposition of sales proceeds and ratifying and confirming prior actions.
